text: Louise Guillet (born 31 January 1986 Limoges) is a French water polo player. == Life == She was captain of the France women's national water polo team at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships. and 2018 Women's European Water Polo Championship. == References == == External links == * Louise Guillet : "Prises en otage par ce conflit" *Lille, the beginning of a long reign?
